-- and where surviving means a desperate confrontation with his own worst fear.</span></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><div class="ChipList"><ul class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--ul"><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/mystery" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Mystery</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/thriller" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Thriller</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/crime" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Crime</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/mystery-thriller" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Mystery Thriller</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/suspense" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Suspense</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/horses" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Horses</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/detective" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Detective</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/british-literature" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">British Literature</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/horse-racing" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Horse Racing</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="BookDetails"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--div"><div class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">304 pages, Paperback</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published January 1, 1979</p><p data-testid="awards"><span class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--span"><span class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><span data-testid="award"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/3816-edgar-award">Edgar Award</a>, Best Novel<span class="Text Text__subdued"> (1981)</span></span>,</span><span class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><span data-testid="award"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/21151-cwa-gold-dagger-award">CWA Gold Dagger Award</a>, Fiction<span class="Text Text__subdued"> (1979)</span></span></span></span></p></div></div><div class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems_